OL,3,CArctic air brings cold snap to UK with
OL,4,Cfrost and snow in some areas
OL,6,FWords by Weather Presenter Jo Blythe
OL,8,FDespite bursts of Spring sunshine, for
OL,9,Fmany parts of the UK it's felt more
OL,10,Flike winter in recent days.
OL,12,FThe UK is now in the middle of a cold
OL,13,Fsnap - here's why.
OL,15,FWhy have temperatures suddenly dropped
OL,16,Fagain?
OL,18,FAway from the sunny spells, the reason
OL,19,Fbehind the chilly feel is where our
OL,20,Fair is coming from.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
