OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778515869
OL,3,CArctic air brings cold snap to UK with
OL,4,Cfrost and snow in some areas
OL,6,FA northerly airflow is bringing Arctic
OL,7,Fair down across the UK, so despite
OL,8,Fsunshine being fairly strong at this
OL,9,Ftime of year, the air feels much
OL,10,Fchillier.
OL,12,FIt has been especially cool along the
OL,13,FNorth Sea coasts.
OL,15,FIt looks like we'll need to reach for
OL,16,Four winter coats as this airflow will
OL,17,Ftravel south until the end of the week.
OL,19,FA chance of frost
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
