PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778515869
OL,3,CArctic air brings cold snap to UK with
OL,4,Cfrost and snow in some areas
OL,6,FGardeners and growers will need to
OL,7,Fcontinue to protect delicate plants as
OL,8,Frural temperatures are set to dip at
OL,9,Fnight.
OL,11,FA minimum temperature of -3.2C was
OL,12,Frecorded in Oxfordshire on Sunday
OL,13,Fnight, and we could see similar
OL,14,Ftemperatures on Monday, wherever there
OL,15,Fare clear skies.
OL,17,FWith low pressure in charge and
OL,18,Fshowers expected over the coming days,
OL,19,Fthere could even be some light
OL,20,Fsnowfall over the Scottish mountains.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
